Personalized food tour!
Jul 2023 • Solo
I had such a blast with Vu! He is so sweet and really thoughtful about how he runs his tours - I mentioned there was a food I wanted to try and he changed up the plan to accommodate me! He took me to places I definitely wouldn’t have known about on my own, and at nearly each place, he took me to where the dishes were made so I could learn the process. I would absolutely urge anyone to book this experience!!
Review of: Hoi An hidden food evening adventure
