Great guide - Mr. Trấn Nguyễn. Thoroughly enjoyed it.
Fantastic. One of my favourite tours in Vietnam so far (this is my second time visiting the country).
The main reason for my experience was my outstanding tour guide Trấn Nguyễn.
He is knowledgeable and so much fun to talk to. I also learnt some interesting insights about Vietnamese society today.
He took some amazing photos of me which I will treasure.
